       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI62306.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI62306.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Emiss緌 Ficha Cadastro Pessoal
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
